window.bookSummaryJSON = "Private space flight has long been a science-fiction dream. Today it is on the verge of realisation. Major entrepreneurs, such as the founders of Virgin, Microsoft, and Amazon, are investing in a new generation of lightweight, efficient spacecraft; start-up companies specialising in space tourism and spaceport development are burgeoning; and NASA and American aviation authorities are altering decades-old legislation to make private space adventure possible. <p><i>How To Build Your Own Spaceship</i> tells you how to join the new space race, where the sky is no longer the limit.</p>"; 
